{"tid":1309611,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇波台手足係操偶師？","createTime":"2019-07-12T09:33:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T11:19:44.000Z","uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8f1beb851d0079730c5aa4cd70b95f0189500e74","tid":1309611,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T09:33:08.000Z","msg":"高雄市觀光局6日推出「港都快閃」活動，「市府網紅」在高雄各地進行快閃。高雄市長韓國瑜則擔任神秘嘉賓，在店家休息時，突然起身抓起吉祥物的頭髮撞了三下；此舉引發爭議，製作吉祥物「高捷少女小芎」的布偶工作室在粉專發文，指出此舉不只會造成偶裝破損，裡面的<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">操偶師</span></span>也可能因此受傷；對此，韓國瑜表示，不知道這樣撞會有後遺症，「我只是希望大家能夠喜歡我們」。"},{"pid":"eee80389648d8466eea902137d913d540b98104c","tid":1309611,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T09:34:39.000Z","msg":"我餐具衞生師"},{"pid":"0cb8bf928ccd09a007a44fa91b0295b047696b0f","tid":1309611,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T09:39:53.000Z","msg":"六隊"},{"pid":"ab6c51670d52290c997426b14f332bf4944ed6ca","tid":1309611,"uid":26959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0cb8bf928ccd09a007a44fa91b0295b047696b0f","tid":1309611,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T09:39:53.000Z","msg":"六隊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T09:48:27.000Z","msg":"哋屎"},{"pid":"185c4800c26888baadf1f66c5bb29273862e16ec","tid":1309611,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T11:19:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}